The paper discusses a methodology and set of tools for constructing applications from components, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also focuses on separating transmission policy from component implementation, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses how inter-address-space parameter passing semantics may be decided independently of component implementation, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and deep learning (cs.DL).
